        <item>
            <title>Version 0.10.0</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 00:35:45 +1000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>New</h3>
<ul>
<li>Ignore sessions by agent, terminal, or individual — inline bell toggle on each session row</li>
<li>Dedicated Ignore settings tab</li>
<li>Customize session row tags (visibility and style)</li>
<li>Task tracking with automatic ID assignment and startup restore</li>
<li>Beta Updates opt-in via Settings > Lab</li>
</ul>
<h3>Improved</h3>
<ul>
<li>Session metadata cached in PID store — faster startup</li>
</ul>
<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Smooth pill open/close transitions</li>
<li>WezTerm jump restored</li>
<li>Notch edge hover no longer flickers</li>
<li>Prevents duplicate bridge instances when app relaunches</li>
<li>Subagent messages no longer overwrite parent session status</li>
<li>Sparkle update window detection more reliable</li>
</ul>]]></description>
